1
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:45,979
[Love of the Divine Tree]

2
00:01:46,630 --> 00:01:48,990
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,080
Let me ask you.

4
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,200
In the past few days,

5
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:52,710
have you eaten Madam Wu's buns?

6
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,200
I have.

7
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:55,810
What connection do you have

8
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:57,000
with those Elite Armored Guard

9
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:59,070
who have gone missing in the past few days?

10
00:01:59,070 --> 00:01:59,930
Five years ago,

11
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,590
we all served on

12
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,790
a border defence unit

13
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,440
for half a month.

14
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:04,920
In this unit,

15
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,080
besides you,

16
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,710
how many more are still alive?

17
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:08,710
There's one more,

18
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,810
Captain Qin.

19
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,190
Alright.

20
00:02:46,590 --> 00:02:48,000
Join them in death!

21
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:53,560
Activate the formation.

22
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,120
Yes.

23
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,170
Master,

24
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,600
leave it to me.

25
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,150
What's on her is resentment.

26
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,560
Formations against demons wouldn't work.

27
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,910
Switch to one that works on humans.

28
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:22,240
From Earth and Thunder to Heaven and Fire!

29
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,600
Obliterate all evil,

30
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:42,630
four Qi condense!

31
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:12,960
Coal.

32
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,800
Coal.

33
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,630
Coal.

34
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,060
Coal is indeed a demon.

35
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,240
Everything it did

36
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,830
was to save you.

37
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:26,830
It discovered early on that the fish demon was harming people.

38
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,000
Damaging the compass

39
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,040
was also to lure the Immortal Master

40
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,370
to come and save people.

41
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,100
No matter what,

42
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,560
it protected

43
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:42,210
the person it wanted to protect the most.

44
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,630
Coal

45
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,070
was like family to me.

46
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,400
Yesterday, when I made you reveal your demon form,

47
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,810
I was really afraid.

48
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:04,180
I feared you might actually harm people.

49
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:06,800
But I never thought

50
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,690
you'd be so foolish.

51
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,070
How could you

52
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:18,360
risk your life for me?

53
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,270
It's a pity

54
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,970
that we're still two people short.

55
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,570
So it is indeed Madam Wu.

56
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,240
Godmother?

57
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,480
Why is it you?

58
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,780
Don't call me godmother anymore.

59
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:04,250
Did you really think I opened this inn

60
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,160
to look at you all

61
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,320
reminiscing my son?

62
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:09,040
Let me tell you.

63
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,410
Every time I see

64
00:06:10,410 --> 00:06:11,510
people from your camp,

65
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,840
I have only one thought.

66
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:14,880
And that is revenge.

67
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,240
I want to avenge

68
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,720
my son!

69
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:24,480
Godmother,

70
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,830
Brother Wu's death was an accident!

71
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:29,190
Back then in the Death Realm,

72
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:30,950
that giant python was too powerful.

73
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,560
Brother Wu died

74
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,060
because he...

75
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:32,740
Nonsense!

76
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:35,430
These are all lies made up by

77
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,270
those people

78
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,270
who harmed my son.

79
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,560
How could it be?

80
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,210
They confessed the truth after drinking,

81
00:06:42,210 --> 00:06:43,480
and I heard it with my own ears.

82
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,610
How could it be fake?

83
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,240
My poor son,

84
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,950
he was only fifteen.

85
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,850
Seeing how hard I worked every day,

86
00:06:54,850 --> 00:06:55,560
washing and cooking,

87
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,690
he lied about his age

88
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,800
to join the army at Wangxiang Pass,

89
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,720
just to earn some money

90
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:04,290
so I wouldn't have to work so hard.

91
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,480
He was still so young.

92
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:11,440
The armor didn't even fit him properly.

93
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,800
He was so happy when he came back.

94
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,850
He told me

95
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:18,800
everyone in the camp was kind to him,

96
00:07:19,430 --> 00:07:21,560
and he even gained a few good brothers.

97
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:26,610
But it was these very brothers

98
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,920
who in the Death Realm

99
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,950
pushed him out to feed the giant python,

100
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,570
stepping on his corpse

101
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,000
to saved their own lives.

102
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,260
Qin Xuanjiu,

103
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,860
although you weren't there that day,

104
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,390
as an officer,

105
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:50,320
you let my son meet such an unfortunate end.

106
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,950
You deserve to die too!

107
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,000
Don't think that

108
00:07:57,530 --> 00:07:59,120
showing concern for me every day

109
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,520
and calling me godmother

110
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,920
can compensate for my son's life.

111
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,360
My son's remains

112
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,670
are still left alone in the Death Realm.

113
00:08:10,690 --> 00:08:12,550
If you truly see me as your mother,

114
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:14,680
why don't you bring him back to me?

115
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:15,720
I've tried,

116
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:18,350
but that giant python in the Death Realm...

117
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,830
These are all excuses.

118
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,560
None of you

119
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,390
will help me.

120
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:38,750
Only immortals will lend me their power.

121
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,030
Immortals?

122
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,270
Yes.

123
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,750
They are

124
00:08:47,310 --> 00:08:49,430
real immortals!

125
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,790
All of you

126
00:08:58,630 --> 00:09:02,150
will eventually be killed by the immortals.

127
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,670
Godmother!

128
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:21,530
Where did this rune come from?

129
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,960
If I can't see my son's remains,

130
00:09:29,470 --> 00:09:31,060
no matter what you ask,

131
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:33,480
I will not

132
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:35,120
utter

133
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,750
another word.

134
00:09:40,810 --> 00:09:43,270
Could it be that Spirit Spring used this rune

135
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:45,450
to transfer resentment onto Madam Wu?

136
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,690
The rune truly is Spirit Spring's tactic.

137
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,120
It's almost dawn.

138
00:09:50,390 --> 00:09:52,440
Let's bring her back to the camp first.

139
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,510
Yes, Master.

140
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,400
Su Yishui indeed didn't disappoint me.

141
00:09:58,390 --> 00:09:59,790
The clue to Spirit Spring

142
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,240
is right before our eyes.

143
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,580
What will happen to Madam Wu next?

144
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,130
After all, lives were lost.

145
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,900
The imperial court

146
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:10,600
will surely send someone to investigate.

147
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,240
Mr. Qin,

148
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:12,970
Madam Wu's son

149
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,200
was indeed murdered.

150
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,270
Her desire to revenge made her ill-minded,

151
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,870
and caused her to be possessed by an evil being.

152
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,200
We need to investigate further

153
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,670
to find out what kind of evil being it is

154
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,630
that could amplify a person's resentment

155
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,670
to such an extent.

156
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,480
I know Madam Wu's personality well.

157
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:27,670
If we couldn't find Brother Wu's remains,

158
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:29,670
Madam Wu wouldn't reveal anything.

159
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,240
But the Death Realm

160
00:10:32,860 --> 00:10:35,060
isn't a place we can simply go as we like.

161
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:38,600
Break!

162
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,390
What's that?

163
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:43,710
Just a passing spirit creature.

164
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,390
Master,

165
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,750
is it Wei Jiu?

166
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:50,280
You seem to recognize him.

167
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,980
The incident at Wangxiang Pass

168
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:53,200
is related to the root of all evil,

169
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,150
the Spirit Spring.

170
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:55,280
How do you know this?

171
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,790
Since that time at Mount Absolute,

172
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,470
Wei Jiu has been searching for the Spirit Spring.

173
00:10:58,470 --> 00:10:59,910
His sudden appearance here

174
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:01,360
must also be for the Spirit Spring.

175
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:01,870
Master,

176
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:04,120
as your direct disciple,

177
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,870
I'm willing to carry out your will.

178
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:06,670
I only allow you to investigate

179
00:11:06,670 --> 00:11:08,090
the case at Wangxiang Pass.

180
00:11:08,090 --> 00:11:09,600
The rest is none of your business.

181
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,530
Master, you see,

182
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:12,310
Wei Jiu has just seen me.

183
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:13,720
There's no guarantee he won't target me

184
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,650
to threaten you.

185
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,410
Hence,

186
00:11:15,770 --> 00:11:16,840
it's better for me to stay by your side

187
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,910
and investigate the Spirit Spring together.

188
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,170
That way, I'll be safe.

189
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,480
It's actually simple to prevent Wei Jiu from acting.

190
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,150
You just have to return to Mount Wester

191
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,480
once the case is solved.

192
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,270
Su Yishui,

193
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,600
I must collect

194
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,910
the debt you owe.

195
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,860
The Crown Prince has arrived.

196
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,210
Qin Xuanjiu, guard of Wangxiang Pass,

197
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,630
greets Your Highness.

198
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,600
No need for formalities.

199
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,980
Sovereign Su, why brings you here

200
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:49,090
to Wangxiang Pass?

201
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,250
Young Master Yu,

202
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:53,240
we descended the mountain for training

203
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,240
and happened to encounter a demon harming people

204
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,410
at Wangxiang Pass,

205
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:56,220
so we came over.

206
00:11:56,220 --> 00:11:57,150
That's perfect.

207
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:58,920
Our last meeting was brief.

208
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,840
Since you're here for training this time,

209
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,390
you might as well accompany me.

210
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:03,120
My disciple's training

211
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,320
is naturally with me.

212
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:06,950
It has nothing to do with Your Highness.

213
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,320
Master,

214
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:11,250
did you just allow me to accompany you?

215
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,480
Captain Qin,

216
00:12:15,230 --> 00:12:17,160
keep the humans under close watch.

217
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:20,080
Demons are the ones harming humans,

218
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:22,480
yet you want to keep the humans under watch?

219
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,200
Feng.

220
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:35,270
Disciple

221
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,120
pays respects to Master.

222
00:12:37,350 --> 00:12:39,870
Captain Qin is Qingge's disciple?

223
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:40,840
Yes.

224
00:12:41,390 --> 00:12:42,150
You are...

225
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:43,840
My name is Qin Xuanjiu.

226
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,560
Twenty years ago,

227
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,600
Master saved my life

228
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,760
on the battlefield.

229
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,530
That's how I became your disciple.

230
00:12:50,530 --> 00:12:52,330
After Master's reincarnation,

231
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:55,590
I have gone to the palace to look for you.

232
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:58,960
So you’re the one who only memorized the names of immortal arts

233
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,820
but never actually learned them?

234
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:01,510
Yes.

235
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,870
I had too many disciples in my past life.

236
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:05,050
I can't remember them all.

237
00:13:05,050 --> 00:13:06,670
Since you haven't learned any immortal arts,

238
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:08,670
you're not considered my disciple.

239
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,460
He's indeed a half-human, half-demon.

240
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:18,390
He's the person we're looking for.

241
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,200
Since soldiers in the army are killed,

242
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,910
it is a matter for the imperial court.

243
00:13:24,910 --> 00:13:25,440
Guards!

244
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:28,250
Take the prisoner back to the capital.

245
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:28,960
Yes.

246
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:29,790
Wait.

247
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:34,750
What is your purpose, Sovereign Su?

248
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:35,910
Evil spirits causing troubles

249
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,360
have always been handled by the Heavenly Gate.

250
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,360
Such a strange case of a half-human, half-demon

251
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,870
furthermore shouldn't be taken lightly.

252
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:42,790
Crown Prince, you've overstepped your bounds.

253
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:45,340
Sovereign Su, you may be domineering on Mount Wester,

254
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,740
but in the military camp,

255
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:48,710
do you have to be so overbearing too?

256
00:13:48,710 --> 00:13:49,790
The Crown Prince says one word

257
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,000
and the person is being taken away.

258
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,400
Who's more overbearing?

259
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:55,200
Master,

260
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,370
Young Master Yu,

261
00:13:56,390 --> 00:13:57,520
I have a suggestion.

262
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,390
Madam Wu wasn't originally a demon,

263
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:00,150
but suddenly became

264
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,610
half-human, half-demon.

265
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:02,600
The urgent matter at hand

266
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,400
is to find out why this happened.

267
00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:06,200
Since Young Master Yu wants to investigate,

268
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,510
and Master wants to investigate too,

269
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:09,030
why don't we do it here at Wangxiang Pass?

270
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:10,200
If we could make this clear,

271
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,630
there's no need to distinguish between

272
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:13,510
the Heavenly Gate and the imperial court.

273
00:14:13,510 --> 00:14:14,040
Alright.

274
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,790
We'll do as Ranran suggests.

275
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:17,390
I hope that within a few days,

276
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,280
there can be some progress.

277
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:23,600
Don't worry, Yu.

278
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,490
With the Exotic Pavilion here,

279
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,480
with Shui here,

280
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:28,200
and with me here as well,

281
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:30,270
we'll surely find a way to make her speak.

282
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:31,270
Master Mu wants to

283
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:32,690
force a confession?

284
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,290
What's wrong with that?

285
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:35,910
Didn't she cause deaths?

286
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,910
I beg for Master's mercy.

287
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,910
Madam Wu was possessed by an evil spirit.

288
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,310
It wasn't her intention.

289
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,440
Madam Wu is physically weak.

290
00:14:46,790 --> 00:14:48,390
She can't endure severe torture.

291
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:50,120
I told you, I'm not your master.

292
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,990
You're pleading for a demon.

293
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:55,060
Do you want to be charged with harboring a criminal?

294
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,720
Prepare to interrogate the prisoner.

295
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,080
Yes.

296
00:15:08,670 --> 00:15:10,270
She refuses to say anything.

297
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:12,240
Yu,

298
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,270
you've had a tiring journey today.

299
00:15:14,270 --> 00:15:16,150
Why don't you go back and rest first?

300
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:17,550
She can't escape anyway.

301
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:31,310
No one has helped me except the immortals.

302
00:15:33,150 --> 00:15:34,510
If I can't find my child,

303
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:38,390
I won't say a single word.

304
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:53,900
Where's Ranran?

305
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:55,740
She said if you want to know

306
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:56,840
the origin of the runes,

307
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,000
you need to find

308
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,600
the corpse of Madam Wu's son.

309
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,130
She also asked me to tell you

310
00:16:03,940 --> 00:16:04,780
not to worry.

311
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:06,240
"I'm very powerful now.

312
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:06,960
I definitely won't

313
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,130
lose to a snake."

314
00:16:13,390 --> 00:16:14,990
Fifty li southwest from here

315
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,210
is the Death Realm!

316
00:16:17,550 --> 00:16:19,090
[Death Realm]

317
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,040
The armored skeleton

318
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,160
is in this direction.

319
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:14,200
[Wu Dayou]

320
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:16,829
On behalf of your mother,

321
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:18,089
I'm bringing you home.

322
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:56,260
Watch me shatter your demon core!

323
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:57,450
Ranran.

324
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,440
Xue Ranran.

325
00:18:08,830 --> 00:18:09,480
Ranran.

326
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:11,510
Master.

327
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:13,510
Master.

328
00:18:14,590 --> 00:18:15,070
Master,

329
00:18:23,550 --> 00:18:25,590
that demon just now was quite formidable.

330
00:18:25,590 --> 00:18:27,250
It almost swallowed me whole.

331
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:28,010
But I thought,

332
00:18:28,010 --> 00:18:29,240
since it was a skeletal python

333
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,170
and had no flesh,

334
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:31,790
what could it do even if it swallowed me?

335
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:32,150
So,

336
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:33,840
I simply crawled into its belly,

337
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:34,960
trailed its bone crevices,

338
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,490
and pierced its demon core.

339
00:18:41,550 --> 00:18:42,030
Master,

340
00:18:43,110 --> 00:18:44,310
I have made a mistake.

341
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:46,440
You're quick to admit your mistake,

342
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:47,570
but you never learn.

343
00:18:49,430 --> 00:18:50,310
I know that

344
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:51,960
Master doesn't allow me to act like this.

345
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,480
But if I could choose again,

346
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,880
I would do the same thing.

347
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:56,340
What?

348
00:18:57,390 --> 00:18:58,790
A immortal cultivator draws their essence

349
00:18:58,790 --> 00:18:59,790
from the universe

350
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:01,280
and should return it in kind.

351
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,000
Upholding justice and rescuing the weak

352
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,480
is the cycle of the Heavenly Way.

353
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,960
Although Madam Wu has harmed people,

354
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,690
her child is the most innocent.

355
00:19:08,330 --> 00:19:09,390
If he saw his mother

356
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,070
in this state,

357
00:19:10,070 --> 00:19:11,270
he would surely be heartbroken.

358
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:12,930
So I brought back his remains,

359
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:14,330
firstly to find clues,

360
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:15,160
and secondly,

361
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:17,090
to fulfill this unfulfilled wish.

362
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:18,330
There are countless people

363
00:19:18,330 --> 00:19:20,060
in this universe who need help.

364
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:22,320
These small acts of kindness

365
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:23,550
are meaningless.

366
00:19:24,350 --> 00:19:26,110
I'll just help as many people as I can.

367
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,910
It's better than doing nothing at all.

368
00:19:27,910 --> 00:19:29,750
If we calculate gains and losses like this,

369
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:30,680
then what's the point

370
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,880
of immortal cultivation training?

371
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:32,480
Am I right?

372
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,110
Yes.

373
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:41,500
Um,

374
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:42,480
Master,

375
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:44,370
I just

376
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,460
thought of some principles

377
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:47,460
and wanted to discuss them with you.

378
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:53,650
This Spirit Dispelling Formation didn't work either.

379
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:55,880
Master, why are you being so polite?

380
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:59,110
Next time when you discuss principles with me,

381
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:01,170
your tone mustn't be disrespectful.

382
00:20:01,410 --> 00:20:01,910
Yes.

383
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:09,350
Let me ask you one last thing.

384
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:10,680
In the future, if you encounter such

385
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:12,610
situations where you have to save people from danger,

386
00:20:12,610 --> 00:20:14,270
but it's extremely perilous,

387
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,460
what should you do?

388
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:16,640
Call Xi'er and the others to help.

389
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:17,070
Wrong.

390
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:27,430
Is it so hard to call for your master's help?

391
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,160
I get it now, Master.

392
00:20:44,950 --> 00:20:45,720
I still couldn't get any information

393
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,160
about the origin of that rune.

394
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,160
That demonic lady

395
00:20:48,270 --> 00:20:49,530
still refuses to talk.

396
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:51,160
But don't worry, Your Highness.

397
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,790
The information you want to know,

398
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:53,440
I

399
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:55,990
will definitely find a way to get it for you.

400
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:58,070
So Yu really wants to know

401
00:20:58,070 --> 00:20:59,550
about that rune.

402
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,750
Whatever punishment you have,

403
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:17,480
just use it all.

404
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,860
Best if you could just kill me,

405
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:22,550
so I can meet see my son.

406
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,720
There's no rush.

407
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:26,130
I haven't heard what I want to hear yet.

408
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:28,200
How could I let you die so easily?

409
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:33,160
What is this?

410
00:21:36,710 --> 00:21:38,000
Why can't I

411
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,470
control my body anymore?

412
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,050
This is called

413
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:42,400
a Marrow-Eating Roach.

414
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:45,150
It loves to burrow into and devour fish brains.

415
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:48,160
I heard you're half-human

416
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,480
and half-fish.

417
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:53,690
You're indeed afraid of it.

418
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,200
Take it away!

419
00:21:55,650 --> 00:21:56,890
Take it away quickly!

420
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:57,550
Sure.

421
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,270
Tell me about the origin

422
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:00,270
of the rune on you,

423
00:22:00,590 --> 00:22:01,790
and I'll take it away.

424
00:22:04,270 --> 00:22:06,070
Just kill me.

425
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:09,030
Seems like you're still not scared enough.

426
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:10,560
Then let's have a taste of it

427
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:11,440
before we talk.

428
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,330
When you can't bear it anymore,

429
00:22:24,330 --> 00:22:25,660
remember to call for me.

430
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:34,910
Still not talking?

431
00:22:56,210 --> 00:22:57,110
You filthy thing.

432
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,510
You're asking for death!

433
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,790
Qingge, what are you doing?

434
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:09,340
Yu,

435
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:10,880
I just wanted to help you

436
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:12,140
to question this demon

437
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,030
Who knew

438
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,000
she would suddenly go berserk

439
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,000
and try to kill me?

440
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,000
You're hurt.

441
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,800
It's just a minor injury.

442
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,760
Then we need to treat it quickly.

443
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:39,920
Something's not right.

444
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:42,800
Why are we still going in circles after so long?

445
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:45,550
Try using your spiritual power.

446
00:23:51,990 --> 00:23:53,720
I can't use my spiritual power.

447
00:23:54,070 --> 00:23:55,330
Why is this happening?

448
00:23:57,310 --> 00:23:58,240
The Death Realm

449
00:23:58,680 --> 00:23:59,410
has changed.

450
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,480
What's going on?

451
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:09,740
Countless beings have perished

452
00:24:09,740 --> 00:24:11,790
in the Death Realm over the centuries.

453
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,680
It was the

454
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,830
giant Bone Python

455
00:24:14,110 --> 00:24:15,460
who kept things in balance.

456
00:24:15,460 --> 00:24:17,030
But now that the Bone Python is dead,

457
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:18,400
all the death energy has been released,

458
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,530
saturating the air,

459
00:24:19,550 --> 00:24:21,480
and obstructing spiritual power.

460
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:23,850
What should we do then?

461
00:24:24,790 --> 00:24:25,320
How about

462
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:27,580
one of us will take in the new,

463
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,790
while the other expels the impurities.

464
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:30,000
If we alternate like this,

465
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,160
we'll be able to use our spiritual power

466
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,290
to leave this place.

467
00:24:32,500 --> 00:24:33,360
So we need to...

468
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:36,940
Hold onto this.

469
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:42,000
Seems like Master also thinks

470
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:43,330
I'm doing the right thing.

471
00:24:43,330 --> 00:24:45,200
Otherwise, why would you let me hold your hand?

472
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:46,330
I'm asking you to...

473
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:55,350
Forget it.

474
00:24:58,690 --> 00:24:59,460
Master,

475
00:25:00,110 --> 00:25:01,110
you're blushing.

476
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,200
Focus.

477
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:28,830
Master.

478
00:25:30,750 --> 00:25:31,550
What's wrong?

479
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,110
Madam Wu is missing.

480
00:25:36,480 --> 00:25:37,000
Ranran,

481
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,510
Madam Wu has died.

482
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:42,030
How could this be?

483
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:45,230
Master interrogated her personally.

484
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,890
I'm not sure why.

485
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:52,020
It was Madam Wu who went mad suddenly.

486
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:55,620
Qingge killed her

487
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,680
under self-defence.

488
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:59,920
Madam Wu was determined to die

489
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:01,320
but was firmly locked up.

490
00:26:01,490 --> 00:26:02,100
How could she have

491
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:03,430
suddenly gone berserk?

492
00:26:04,030 --> 00:26:04,960
Young Master Yu,

493
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,060
where is Master Mu?

494
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,030
I need to get to the bottom of this.

495
00:26:07,030 --> 00:26:08,430
Qingge was injured by her

496
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:09,770
and is now recovering.

497
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,500
Let's not disturb her.

498
00:26:12,770 --> 00:26:13,720
We went through great trouble

499
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,400
to retrieve her son's remains;

500
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,800
we need answers from her.

501
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:18,490
Besides,

502
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:21,110
even if Madam Wu was guilty and deserved punishment,

503
00:26:21,110 --> 00:26:21,750
it should be done through either a public trial,

504
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:23,010
or the Heavenly order.

505
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:25,680
How could Master Mu just kill her without due process?

506
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:26,140
Ranran.

507
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,240
It’s come to this,

508
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:30,600
there’s nothing more that can be done.

509
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:31,920
Besides, when the Heavenly Sects

510
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:34,000
typically encounters a demon like Madam Wu,

511
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,960
they would have killed her long ago,

512
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:36,820
wouldn't they?

513
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:38,810
It was a case where

514
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,710
pleas for karma went unanswered,

515
00:26:40,710 --> 00:26:42,750
that's why Madam Wu sought help from evil spirits,

516
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:44,210
leading to this disaster.

517
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:46,920
Now,

518
00:26:47,750 --> 00:26:49,200
it's still the same.

519
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:53,530
Ranran,

520
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:56,880
I'll allocate a piece of land with good feng shui

521
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,820
for the mother and son to be buried together.

522
00:26:58,820 --> 00:27:00,680
This should put your mind at ease.

523
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:02,040
Is that alright?

524
00:27:03,070 --> 00:27:04,530
Thank you, Your Highness.

525
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:11,360
Acted in self-defence?

526
00:27:19,120 --> 00:27:19,800
All packed up?

527
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:20,530
Let's leave.

528
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:22,770
Don't stay here anymore.

529
00:27:22,770 --> 00:27:23,570
Let's get out.

530
00:27:23,610 --> 00:27:25,010
I heard the owner of this inn

531
00:27:25,010 --> 00:27:25,870
killed someone

532
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:26,930
and was sentenced to death.

533
00:27:26,930 --> 00:27:27,970
It's very unlucky.

534
00:27:27,970 --> 00:27:28,530
Let's leave.

535
00:27:28,530 --> 00:27:28,960
Go.

536
00:27:29,030 --> 00:27:29,640
Go, go, go.

537
00:27:29,720 --> 00:27:30,350
Hurry.

538
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,740
Years of operation

539
00:27:33,190 --> 00:27:35,060
can fall into ruin in an instant.

540
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,640
Where will we stay for the next few days?

541
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,000
There simply is no one here to manage.

542
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:40,640
For us,

543
00:27:41,110 --> 00:27:42,440
it makes no difference.

544
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:47,160
What Master means is

545
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:49,030
that we've all eaten poisoned buns

546
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:50,360
and couldn't fly on our swords,

547
00:27:50,360 --> 00:27:51,660
so we should rest here for a few days

548
00:27:51,660 --> 00:27:52,860
before we can set out.

549
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:56,450
Let's go.

550
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:22,830
Master.

551
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,590
You have accumulated merits

552
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:26,640
and your cultivation has reached the stage of Qi Refinement.

553
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:28,920
You will soon be ready to build Foundation.

554
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:29,720
What's wrong?

555
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,070
I

556
00:28:32,510 --> 00:28:33,550
think I know

557
00:28:33,550 --> 00:28:35,210
what the runes on Madam Wu are.

558
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,770
How did you find out?

559
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,570
I saw through Vine again

560
00:28:38,930 --> 00:28:40,920
and had a glimpse of fragments of my past life.

561
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,920
I saw a book

562
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:43,480
and the runes on it

563
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:45,950
were identical to those on Madam Wu's body.

564
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:48,830
It's called the Seven Evil Transformation Spell.

565
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,480
Can't believe I have forgotten

566
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:51,410
these information from back then.

567
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,610
Seven Evil Transformation Spell.

568
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,680
Celestial Sect.

569
00:28:58,830 --> 00:28:59,750
I see.

570
00:29:00,310 --> 00:29:01,710
What exactly is going on,

571
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:02,480
Master?

572
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:04,510
I've heard that Seven Evil Transformation Spell

573
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:05,790
is powered by resentment

574
00:29:05,790 --> 00:29:07,790
to integrate humans and beasts into demons.

575
00:29:07,790 --> 00:29:08,510
And the resentment generated

576
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:09,480
by these demons

577
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:11,160
can be absorbed back by the spell,

578
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:12,680
creating an endless cycle.

