00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:13,740
The Mortal-Demon Lord back then

580
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:15,140
relied on this evil spell

581
00:29:15,510 --> 00:29:17,030
to accumulate resentment and become a devil,

582
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:19,010
eventually becoming the leader of all devils.

583
00:29:19,010 --> 00:29:20,480
The Spirit Spring is the Mortal-Demon Lord's

584
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:22,000
spiritual power transformed.

585
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:22,640
So,

586
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:25,350
this is a repeat of the old trick.

587
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:26,080
Correct.

588
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,370
The Spirit Spring intends to do the same as before,

589
00:29:28,370 --> 00:29:29,480
accumulating resentment

590
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,480
to break the seal.

591
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,260
What should we do then?

592
00:29:32,550 --> 00:29:34,070
Since it's still harming people,

593
