it means the seal hasn't been broken yet.

594
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,920
We still stand a chance.

595
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:37,720
I know someone

596
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,440
who should be able to use the spell

597
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:41,040
to locate the Spirit Spring.

598
00:29:41,830 --> 00:29:42,360
Alright,

599
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:44,270
none of this matters right now.

600
00:29:44,270 --> 00:29:45,450
You've just advanced.

601
00:29:45,450 --> 00:29:47,000
Quickly focus and stabilize your spiritual power.

602
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:47,800
I'll help you.

603
00:30:03,110 --> 00:30:04,910
Why have these ice walls melted?

604
00:30:06,070 --> 00:30:07,110
My cultivation has advanced.

605
00:30:07,110 --> 00:30:08,350
I can come to see you again.

606
00:30:08,350 --> 00:30:09,750
How have you been lately?

607
00:30:09,820 --> 00:30:10,670
It seems that

608
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:12,240
it has become much warmer here.

609
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:14,170
Has it become easier to endure now?

610
00:30:18,270 --> 00:30:19,130
You don't know,

611
00:30:19,310 --> 00:30:21,330
so many things have happened recently.

612
00:30:21,330 --> 00:30:22,570
I like Master

613
00:30:23,010 --> 00:30:24,410
and it seems he found out.

614
00:30:25,100 --> 00:30:27,110
I thought he wouldn't talk to me anymore,

615
00:30:27,110 --> 00:30:27,970
but guess what,

616
00:30:28,110 --> 00:30:29,770
he's still being so kind to me.

617
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:34,600
Yesterday,

618
00:30:35,040 --> 00:30:37,880
Master played the flute to help me out of a difficult situation.

619
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:40,140
He protected me, afraid I might get hurt.

620
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:42,340
When I went to the Death Realm,

621
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:44,130
he got very angry

622
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,820
and was very worried about me.

623
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:46,960
Do you think

624
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:49,520
Master might

625
00:30:49,550 --> 00:30:50,950
have feelings for me too?

626
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,020
If that's the case,

627
00:30:56,410 --> 00:30:57,070
if I invite Master again

628
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:58,750
to see the Paired Wings Auspicious Clouds,

629
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,290
he would agree, right?

630
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:13,650
When we left the Death Realm today,

631
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:15,480
Master asked me to hold his hand.

632
00:31:16,510 --> 00:31:18,240
Master's hand was really soft.

633
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:19,350
Oh, right!

634
00:31:19,790 --> 00:31:20,590
Master's hand

635
00:31:20,790 --> 00:31:21,790
is on my back right now,

636
00:31:21,790 --> 00:31:22,830
helping me cultivate.

637
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:24,490
I never dared to imagine this!

638
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,350
If only I could be under

639
00:31:27,370 --> 00:31:28,830
the Peach Blossom Intoxication again.

640
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:30,680
The duration last time was too short,

641
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,680
there wasn't enough time to do many things.

642
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:34,480
I wanted to pinch Master's cheeks,

643
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:36,210
but there wasn't time for that.

644
00:31:37,070 --> 00:31:38,750
Would Master's cheek

645
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,350
be as soft as his hand?

646
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,830
Where is Master?

647
00:31:52,670 --> 00:31:54,130
Why did he suddenly leave?

648
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:08,680
You are...

649
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:11,510
May I ask, young lady,

650
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,270
was the person with you earlier

651
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:14,910
really the sovereign of Mount Wester,

652
00:32:14,910 --> 00:32:15,910
Su Yishui?

653
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:16,880
Yes.

654
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,730
Are you looking for Master?

655
00:32:20,550 --> 00:32:21,810
I indeed have some business

656
00:32:21,810 --> 00:32:23,310
and need to see Sovereign Su.

657
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:24,510
Please wait a moment.

658
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:28,220
Master.

659
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:29,380
I'm not around.

660
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,000
Um,

661
00:32:36,420 --> 00:32:37,880
