662
00:32:38,780 --> 00:32:39,240
Come in.

663
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:49,920
We don't seem to know each other.

664
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:52,450
Although Sovereign Su doesn't recognize me,

665
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:54,030
for the past ten years,

666
00:32:54,030 --> 00:32:56,090
I've been to Mount Wester many times.

667
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:57,300
Unfortunately,

668
00:32:57,300 --> 00:32:58,900
the gates were always closed

669
00:32:59,070 --> 00:33:00,720
and I never had the chance to meet you.

670
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,270
Today,

671
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:04,010
running into Sovereign Su at Wangxiang Pass

672
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:06,070
must be heaven's will.

673
00:33:07,750 --> 00:33:09,640
I've been entrusted by an old friend

674
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:12,070
to bring something to Sovereign Su.

675
00:33:13,270 --> 00:33:15,230
I've long since cut ties with the mortal world

676
00:33:15,230 --> 00:33:16,920
and I don't accept things from others.

677
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:19,180
This old friend of mine is not a stranger.

678
00:33:19,270 --> 00:33:20,470
Her surname is Jiang,

679
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,960
and she's Sovereign Su's

680
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:24,030
inseparable blood relative.

681
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,480
Many years ago,

682
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:30,810
I once held you

683
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:32,030
at the Rouge Chamber.

684
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:34,680
This old friend of mine is

685
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,350
your mother.

686
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:39,100
Sister Jiang

687
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:41,270
died of illness at Wangxiang Pass.

688
00:33:41,830 --> 00:33:43,160
Before she passed away,

689
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:46,110
she mustered all her strength

690
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,840
to ask me to pass you this key.

691
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:50,890
She said you have to

692
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,720
visit her final accommodation.

693
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:54,370
There's no need.

694
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,640
Ranran, see the guest out.

695
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:56,350
Yishui,

696
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:59,000
I know her personality well.

697
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,790
What happened to you back then

698
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:02,720
doesn't seem like something she would do.

699
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:03,370
After she passed away,

700
00:34:03,370 --> 00:34:04,960
I often came to pay my respects.

701
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,590
Yesterday

702
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:09,000
happened to be the anniversary of her death.

703
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:10,900
I'm not forcing you

704
00:34:10,900 --> 00:34:12,449
to acknowledge this family tie again,

705
00:34:12,449 --> 00:34:12,969
Yishui.

706
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:14,000
At least

707
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:16,320
take this key and pay a visit

708
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:17,739
to fulfill her last wish.

709
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,030
Ranran,

710
00:34:20,850 --> 00:34:21,850
see the guest out.

711
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:27,150
Madam.

712
00:34:28,350 --> 00:34:29,909
I once heard Madam Wu

713
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:31,650
mumbling when drunk,

714
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:33,440
if she could start over,

715
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:36,590
she wouldn't let her son join the army.

716
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:40,580
The world is full of accidents and misfortunes.

717
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,260
If you're not careful,

718
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:45,000
you might regret it for life.

719
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,110
This key,

720
00:34:50,590 --> 00:34:51,650
I'll leave it here.

721
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,110
As for

722
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:55,080
whether you go

723
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:56,880
or not...

724
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:12,000
Master!

725
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:33,170
Master actually does care a lot, doesn't he?

726
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:35,670
I better piece the key back together

727
00:35:35,700 --> 00:35:37,900
and ask about the location of the grave.

728
00:35:38,010 --> 00:35:38,810
If someday

729
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:40,240
Master changes his mind,

730
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:42,440
at least he'll know where to find it.

731
00:35:43,130 --> 00:35:46,840
[Madam Wu's Inn]

732
00:35:56,030 --> 00:35:56,760
Show it to me.

733
00:36:02,250 --> 00:36:04,710
You're becoming more and more disobedient.

734
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,810
You spent the entire night

735
00:36:07,810 --> 00:36:08,710
searching for these fragments

736
00:36:08,710 --> 00:36:09,510
piece by piece

737
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:10,490
in the river?

738
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:11,510
Yes.

739
00:36:12,150 --> 00:36:13,450
Your cultivation is still unstable,

740
00:36:13,450 --> 00:36:14,480
yet you waste your energy

741
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,320
on these trivial matters.

742
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:16,710
Throw them away immediately and go back to meditate.

743
00:36:16,710 --> 00:36:17,070
No.

744
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:22,710
You want to be punished?

745
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:23,840
Even if I'm punished,

746
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,370
I can't throw away this key.

747
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,210
The lady said

748
00:36:27,390 --> 00:36:29,880
the world is full of accidents and misfortunes.

749
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:31,540
I'm afraid she might be right.

750
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,270
You're getting bolder and bolder.

751
00:36:34,270 --> 00:36:34,920
You dare to start meddling

752
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,250
in my personal affairs?

753
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:37,910
I wouldn't dare, Master.

754
00:36:40,140 --> 00:36:41,940
I'm just afraid to see you upset.

755
00:36:42,590 --> 00:36:43,230
Today, when Master

756
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,440
threw away the key,

757
00:36:45,150 --> 00:36:47,610
you were actually quite upset, weren't you?

758
00:36:49,590 --> 00:36:50,590
Do you really know

759
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,190
if I’m upset?

760
00:36:53,110 --> 00:36:54,800
Everything about you, Master,

761
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,000
I care deeply about.

762
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:59,130
I don't know what happened in the past,

763
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:01,070
I'm just concerned

764
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:03,320
that If there are any regrets,

765
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:05,720
there should be a chance to clarify things.

766
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:09,140
Regrets are regrets.

767
00:37:10,510 --> 00:37:12,040
We didn’t meet while alive,

768
00:37:12,510 --> 00:37:14,910
