782
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,440
Madam Jiang died of illness.

783
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:25,960
Judging from the handwriting,

784
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:26,550
she must have used

785
00:38:26,550 --> 00:38:28,550
her last ounce of strength to write.

786
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:31,040
She begged someone to bring the key to Master,

787
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,460
[To Shui]

788
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:32,070
but not

789
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:33,670
the letter and box directly.

790
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:35,280
There must be a hidden story.

791
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:37,440
No.

792
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:38,670
I still need to ask Master

793
00:38:38,670 --> 00:38:40,200
to come and see for himself.

794
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:41,880
But forcing Master

795
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,340
is really inappropriate.

796
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:44,660
I've got it.

797
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:47,730
Master, save me!

798
00:38:57,290 --> 00:38:58,360
I told you to shout "Master, save me!"

799
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,280
for your own protection.

800
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,940
How dare you use it to trick me?

801
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:02,390
I know it's not right.

802
00:39:02,510 --> 00:39:03,770
Take a look at this box.

803
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:25,360
Master,

804
00:39:26,510 --> 00:39:29,240
this porcelain bottle is bone-chillingly cold.

805
00:39:29,250 --> 00:39:31,150
Madam Jiang had no immortal powers.

806
00:39:31,150 --> 00:39:32,280
Carrying this thing

807
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:34,280
would surely cause her to be plagued by severe illness.

808
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,550
Perhaps this is why...

809
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:40,530
she called you here to take a look.

810
00:39:40,930 --> 00:39:41,590
She must have

811
00:39:41,590 --> 00:39:43,120
left some important words.

812
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,280
Shui,

813
00:40:00,130 --> 00:40:01,670
as I write this first sentence,

814
00:40:01,670 --> 00:40:02,870
I'm already thinking

815
00:40:03,910 --> 00:40:04,910
that you probably

816
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,890
will never see this letter.

817
00:40:08,190 --> 00:40:09,320
But I have no choice.

818
00:40:10,150 --> 00:40:11,480
I can only take a gamble,

819
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,920
betting that I can use my life

820
00:40:14,450 --> 00:40:15,390
to free my dear Shui

821
00:40:15,390 --> 00:40:17,120
from the torment of evil magic.

822
00:40:17,770 --> 00:40:19,160
Because this is the sin

823
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:20,990
I committed out of presumption.

824
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:24,000
Before Prince Ping took you away,

825
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:24,840
he came to me.

826
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:27,320
He said he'd give me a sum of money

827
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:29,650
to let you be a young master in his mansion.

828
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:32,150
Of course I wanted the money,

829
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:36,300
but I also wanted you to live a life better than mine.

830
00:40:38,070 --> 00:40:39,710
He feared you wouldn't comply,

831
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:41,710
