832
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:43,580
That is why, from that time on,

833
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:45,720
I became cold towards you

834
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,290
and harsh on you.

835
00:40:49,710 --> 00:40:51,280
I listened to your father's words

836
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,940
and must never recognize you.

837
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,890
Until his military defeat,

838
00:40:56,770 --> 00:40:58,370
I was very worried about you,

839
00:40:58,480 --> 00:41:01,680
but I overheard his conversation with his subordinates.

840
00:41:03,550 --> 00:41:05,710
Three provinces have been lost in succession.

841
00:41:05,710 --> 00:41:07,030
What are Your Highness's

842
00:41:07,030 --> 00:41:07,920
