843
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:08,890
What plans?

844
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:10,440
You're all a bunch of useless fools.

845
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:10,920
Get out!

846
00:41:12,230 --> 00:41:12,760
Yes.

847
00:41:26,150 --> 00:41:27,230
Su Yishui,

848
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:32,180
if you little brat still refuse to summon the Spirit Spring

849
00:41:33,630 --> 00:41:36,230
and insist on saving some Mu Qingge...

850
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:39,480
Fine,

851
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:42,190
it doesn't matter.

852
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:44,590
As long as I have this in hand,

853
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:46,960
I can certainly make you

854
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:49,070
